        <abstract>
            <p>He has heard CD is about to be elected to the Académie des Sciences.</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi>, with its emphasis on insect pollination, helps explain the problem he has worked on for so long: i.e., the rapid diversification of angiosperms in the fossil record occurs in conjunction with the diversification of insects.</p> 
        </abstract>
